# ============================================================
# TimeMachine Backup - Server List
# ============================================================
# List of servers to back up, one per line.
# Format: <hostname> [OPTIONS]
#
# Options:
#   --files-only   Only backup files (skip database dump)
#   --db-only      Only backup databases (skip file sync)
#   --no-rotate    Skip backup rotation for this host
#
# Lines starting with # are comments.
# Blank lines are ignored.
#
# This file is executed in parallel by daily-runner.sh.
# The number of parallel jobs is controlled by TM_PARALLEL_JOBS
# in your .env configuration.
# ============================================================

# === Critical Production Servers ===
# web1.example.com
# db1.example.com
# app1.example.com

# === File-Only Servers (no database) ===
# relay1.example.com --files-only
# monitor1.example.com --files-only

# === Database-Only Servers ===
# db-replica1.example.com --db-only

# === DNS / Infrastructure ===
# ns1.example.com --files-only
# ns2.example.com --files-only
